dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Valleton quadrangle, Monterey County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Arlie M. Skov Honorary Map. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Valleton CA 1948. Photorevised 1973. AMS 1855 I NW - series V895." "First printing, February 2007." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent field work 2003. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1974.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
